---
---

<section class="section-newsletter">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="nl-wrap">

      <div class="nl-content">
        <span class="label-kicker">Every Tuesday · Free</span>
        <h2>GET THE<br>WEEKLY <em>DROP.</em></h2>
        <p>One curated email each week: the launches worth your money, the deals worth your time, and the editorial reviews you won't find anywhere else. Zero noise.</p>

        <form
          class="nl-form"
          id="nlForm"
          onsubmit="(function(f){f.preventDefault();var inp=f.querySelector('input'),btn=f.querySelector('button');btn.innerHTML='&#10003; Subscribed';btn.style.background='var(--success)';btn.style.color='white';inp.disabled=true;})(this)"
        >
          <input type="email" placeholder="your@email.com" required>
          <button type="submit">
            Subscribe
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4">
              <path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" />
            </svg>
          </button>
        </form>

        <div class="nl-perks">
          <span class="nl-perk">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4"><path d="M5 12l5 5L20 7"/></svg>
            47,000+ subscribers
          </span>
          <span class="nl-perk">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4"><path d="M5 12l5 5L20 7"/></svg>
            5-min read
          </span>
          <span class="nl-perk">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4"><path d="M5 12l5 5L20 7"/></svg>
            Unsubscribe anytime
          </span>
        </div>

        <p class="nl-fine">
          By subscribing, you agree to receive marketing from asmaz. We respect your privacy — see our <a href="/policies/privacy-policy">privacy policy</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="nl-side">
        <div class="nl-side-card">
          <span class="stamp">Issue 247</span>
          <div class="issue">Tuesday · This Week</div>
          <h3>THE WEEKLY DROP &amp; 6 LAUNCHES.</h3>
          <ul class="preview-list">
            <li>30 days with this week's flagship pick — verdict inside.</li>
            <li>The camera selling out across every store — here's why.</li>
            <li>6 new launches we tested before publishing.</li>
            <li>Editor's deal of the week (subscribers only).</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="footer">
            <span>Read by 47,000+ shoppers</span>
            <span>5 min read</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
